edu.nd.darts.cimon
Class MMSService

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.MetricService<Long>
      edu.nd.darts.cimon.MMSService
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObservableUpdate
public final class MMSService
extends MetricService<Long>

Monitoring service for MMS activity. Monitors count of sent and received MMS messages. Since database URLs for telephony services are not made public by Android and not supported, this is not guaranteed to work going forward.
MMS metrics:

  • Sent MMS count
  • Received MMS count

    Author:
    darts
